          Auto-merging nitfol
          CONFLICT (content): Merge conflict in nitfol
          Automatic merge failed; fix conflicts and then commit the result.
          $ git reset --hard                 (2)
          $ git pull . topic/branch          (3)
          Updating from 41223... to 13134...
          Fast-forward
